list.title: PAIN IS TEMPORARY Motivational Speech
list.description:
PAIN IS TEMPORARY Motivational Speech is a non-dramatic, conversational style of speech that helps you get traction on your goals and success.

You'll hear how pain is temporary and will see examples of pain that you can use to help you reach your goals.

Designed to help you get motivated, PAIN IS TEMPORARY Motivational Speech will help you change your life and your behavior.
